      <title>据报道英特尔将成为收购目标，股价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/intel-shares-jump-on-report-it-s-an-acquisition-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一家科技新闻网站报道称，陷入困境的芯片制造商英特尔公司 (Intel Corp.) 已成为收购目标，此后该公司股价周五上午一度上涨 9.5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/intel-shares-jump-on-report-it-s-an-acquisition-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 14:34:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
